reviewText: Saw this in person earlier this year and had to have this dvd to watch it again...and again...and again!!
Perfect for the Buckeye fan and Alum that I am

As an Ohio State fan, you can never get enough of The Ohio State University's football team handing out a beatdown! I thought that this was the National Championship game, but it was cool to see Notre Dame catch it on the chin!

I wasn't able to watch this bowl game live and only saw the highlights on the sports channels after the fact, so this dvd allowed me to watch the entire game. I found the game was much more closely contested after Joey Bosa was ejected.
Exactly as described. Fast shipment. Well packed. Great price.
Being a Ohio state buckeyes fan
